---------------------------------------
Restart Centos Terminal
setenforce 0 (menonaktifkan SELinux)
/opt/lampp/lampp/start
service httpd start
service tomcat6 start

reboot -h now

Open Port :
iptables -A INPUT -m state --state NEW -p tcp --dport 8080 -j ACCEPT
/sbin/service iptables save

Eksport database :
psql -H localhost -d nama_database -U postgres -f nama_file_database

Eksport database SQL Server:
sqlcmd -S Sec-Indo03,1433\MSSQLSERVER -U fandeka -P fande ka123 -d hris_timas -i C:\Users\Administrator\Downloads\scriptJan2017.sql
